characterDescription.skinTone: fair skin with subtle pink undertones, especially noticeable on the cheeks. There's a slight unevenness in tone around the eyes and nose.
characterDescription.eyeColor: bright, clear blue eyes with a slightly darker limbal ring. No visible flecks.
characterDescription.eyeShape: large, slightly almond-shaped eyes with a very subtle downturned outer corner. Upper eyelids are partially hooded.
characterDescription.hairColor: medium chestnut brown with subtle lighter brown highlights and reddish undertones. The hair closer to the scalp appears slightly darker.
characterDescription.hairTexture: naturally wavy hair with some loose curls and frizziness. The texture appears soft and fine. Hair is of medium density.
characterDescription.hairStyle: hair styled in two high pigtails, secured with pink hair ties and white pom-pom clips. Bangs are thin and softly curled, just grazing the eyebrows.
characterDescription.faceShape: round face with full, prominent cheeks. Soft jawline and a rounded forehead.
characterDescription.nose: small, slightly upturned nose with a rounded tip. The bridge is slightly sloped.
characterDescription.lips: full, well-defined lips with a natural pink color. The bottom lip appears slightly fuller than the upper lip.
characterDescription.smile: no smile present. Lips are closed in a neutral expression.
characterDescription.eyebrows: medium-thick eyebrows, a shade darker than the hair color. They are naturally arched and softly defined.
characterDescription.ears: medium-sized ears that are mostly obscured by hair, but appear to be close-set to the head.
characterDescription.cheeks: full and round cheeks with a natural rosiness, creating a youthful appearance.
characterDescription.facialProportions: large eyes relative to face size. Small nose and mouth. The lower face is slightly shorter compared to the upper face.
characterDescription.distinctiveFeatures: a small indentation above the right eyebrow. Slight dark circles under the eyes. Faint line of hair on the forehead.
characterDescription.overallImpression: sweet and innocent appearance, youthful baby-faced features. Appears thoughtful or slightly serious.
characterDescription.fullDescription: This is a 5-6 year old girl with a sweet, innocent face. She has fair skin with subtle pink undertones, large, bright blue eyes with a slightly downturned outer corner and medium chestnut brown wavy hair styled in two high pigtails secured with pink hair ties and white pom-pom clips. Her face is round with full cheeks and a rounded, slightly receding chin. She has a small, slightly upturned nose and full, well-defined pink lips. A small indentation is visible above her right eyebrow and there are faint dark circles under her eyes, and thin, lightly curled bangs that just graze the eyebrows.
